#LFC offering no comment on Mohamed Salah's fitness after he appeared to miss training yesterday. Would be a big blow if he's missing - should hear more on that from Jurgen Klopp tomorrow.<br />
<br />
Klopp on the condition of the #LFC squad ahead of Sunday: &ldquo;In the moment, nobody really is ruled out for Sunday, but we have to see.&rdquo;
